  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >注意事项：</h2> 目前仅完成了女主线，男主线仍在制作中。<br>官方游戏群：553769381<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于角色：</h2>澪<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445670/extras/deeee8c528750210116d2e08aaee9a93.avif?t=1604973224\" width=153 height=144 /></span><br>谜之少女。虽然失去了记忆，但却能熟练的使用各种枪械。<br><br>玖<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445670/extras/d6953b03e9ca533b19c4cdfbd2bc251b.avif?t=1604973224\" width=153 height=144 /></span><br>利能研究所安保队成员，奉命前往意识世界调查世界崩坏的原因。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2>1.各种各样的解谜<br><br>2.atb回合制战斗<br>3.刺激的追逐战<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解谜</h2><br>各式各样的解谜<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445670/extras/e16e8dfb083628fefe775f90a9d73a1e.poster.avif?t=1604973224\" width=400 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445670/extras/e16e8dfb083628fefe775f90a9d73a1e.webm?t=1604973224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445670/extras/e16e8dfb083628fefe775f90a9d73a1e.mp4?t=1604973224\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445670/extras/b28d0d920549447df0421f8a62f5951a.poster.avif?t=1604973224\" width=400 height=170 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445670/extras/b28d0d920549447df0421f8a62f5951a.webm?t=1604973224\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1445670/extras/b28d0d920549447df0421f8a62f5951a.mp4?t=1604973224\" type=\"video/mp